Enum SpatialPredicate

    Serializable, Comparable<SpatialPredicate>

    public enum SpatialPredicate
extends Enum<SpatialPredicate>
    Spatial predicates for range queries and join queries. Please refer to Spatial predicates for the semantics of these spatial predicates.
